Review:
This is a sneakerhead dream app. Clean lines and minimalistic design (and most importantly the lack of distracting advertising) lead to a better experience when browsing for purchase or for leisure. The social aspect of seeing how the shoes are on feet on other users is also a great addition, to give a different perspective on the shoes. 

Using the app is ridiculously easy and making purchases are even easier (because there isn't any cart jacking or bad Adidas website load times). You just find the shoe and size (if available), fill in your info, make your purchase and there you go!

